  Minerals Information

                             Statistical Compendium

   This Statistical Compendium provides a consistent set of official,
   long-term (20 years or more) data series through 1990 for selected
   commodities to facilitate analysis of longterm trends in these mineral
   sectors. Listed below is an index of mineral commodity data published
   in the Statistical Compendium. The complete Statistical Compendium is
   available in print and on CD-ROM.
     * Aluminum
     * Bauxite and Alumina
     * Cement
     * Chromium
     * Clays
     * Cobalt
     * Copper
     * Ferroalloys
     * Gold
     * Iron Ore
     * Iron and Steel Scrap
     * Iron and Steel
     * Lead
     * Lime
     * Magnesium
     * Manganese
     * Nickel
     * Phosphate Rock
     * Platinum-Group Metals
     * Rare Earths
     * Salt
     * Sand and Gravel
          + Construction
          + Industrial
     * Silicon
     * Silver
     * Stone, Crushed
     * Soda Ash
     * Sodium Sulfate
     * Sulfur
     * Tin
     * Titanium
     * Tungsten
     * Zinc
     __________________________________________________________________

